<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<title>我的财富</title>
 <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
<script src="http://$request.serverName/js/jquery-2.1.3.min.js"></script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="http://$request.serverName/css/my-wealth.css" type="text/css" />
</head>
<body>
<div id="container">
    <div class="header">
        <a href="http://$request.serverName/user/index" class="header-back btn">
			<img class="img1" src="http://$request.serverName/images/back_n.png">
			<img class="img2" src="http://$request.serverName/images/back_p.png">
		</a>
        <span>我的财富</span>
    </div>
	<div class="header-menu">
		<ul>
			<li>
				<p>可用余额</p>
				<p style="color:#E81959">￥$accountInfo.result.remainingSum</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<p>冻结余额</p>
				<p style="color:#E81959">￥$accountInfo.result.frozenSum</p>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="money">
		<ul>
			<li style="border:1px dashed #6DA6F3">
				<p>累计收入</p>
				<p style="color:#E81959">￥$accountInfo.result.totalEaring</p>
			</li>
			<li style="border:1px dashed #E81959">
				<p>已提现</p>
				<p style="color:#E81959">￥$accountInfo.result.totalWithdraw</p>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="footer-btn">
		<a href="http://$request.serverName/user/withDraw" id="money-btn">我要提现</a>
	</div>
	<div class="footer-tip">
		<p style="color:#E81959">温馨提示：</p>
		<p>可用余额：是已经到账的，可以进行提现的。</p>
		<div class="tip01">冻结佣金：</div><div class="tip02">买家已经购买，但是交易未完成，有可能存在退款的情况，佣金未到账<div>
	</div>
</div>
</body>
<script>
    $(function(){
		$(".btn").click(function(){
			if($(this).find(".img1").is(":visible")){
				$(this).find(".img1").hide();
				$(this).find(".img2").show();
			}else{
				$(this).find(".img1").show();
				$(this).find(".img2").hide();
			}
		});
		
		$("#money-btn").click(function(){
			$(this).css({"color":"#fff","background-color":"#E81959"});
			setTimeout(function(){
				$("#money-btn").css({"color":"#5e5b5c","background-color":"#fff"});
			},1000)
		});
	});
</script>
</html>
 
